The paper deals with image processing, segmentation, and texture analysis, which are all topics related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of thresholding and edge detection techniques also suggests that the paper could be classified under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper could also be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as these fields often involve image analysis and segmentation.
